# IsaacLab -> mjlab Migration Guardrails

- Use `mujocolab/anymal_c_velocity` as the migration pattern.
- Do not modify `mujocolab/mjlab` source.
- Keep behavior equivalent for rewards/obs/actions/commands/reset/termination/curriculum.
- Must be mjlab-native after migration.
- No compat layer, adapter shim, or bridge wrapper.
- No new fallback logic unless source task has it.
- No new `raise`/`assert` unless source task has it.
- Keep source comments/TODO semantics.
- Manager config must be dict-based (`dict[str, XxxTermCfg]`), no manager `@configclass`.
- Remove IsaacLab API remnants after migration.
- Ask user to choose `preserve-layout` or `mjlab-layout` before migration if not specified.
